contestants.name: Jenna Lewis-Dougherty
contestants.bio: 47-year-old from Woodland, California. Jenna first appeared on the inaugural season Survivor: Borneo and returned in Survivor: All Stars; she was voted out just before the Final Tribal Council

contestants.name: Colby Donaldson
contestants.bio: 51-year-old from Austin, Texas. On Survivor: The Australian Outback he became the first contestant to win five Immunity Challenges and finished as runner-up. Colby later returned for All-Stars and Heroes vs. Villains

contestants.name: Stephenie LaGrossa Kendrick
contestants.bio: 45-year-old from Dunedin, Florida. Stephenie competed on Survivor: Palau, where she was the last member of the Ulong tribe. She later returned for Survivor: Guatemala, finishing as runner-up, and appeared on Heroes vs. Villains

contestants.name: Cirie Fields
contestants.bio: 54-year-old from Jersey City, New Jersey. Regarded as one of the best players never to win, Cirie competed on Survivor: Panama, Micronesia, Heroes vs. Villains and Game Changers. She consistently reached the later stages but never captured the title

contestants.name: Ozzy Lusth
contestants.bio: 43-year-old from Guanajuato, Mexico. A legendary challenge competitor, Ozzy dominated Survivor: Cook Islands, winning five immunity challenges and finishing as runner-up. He returned for Micronesia, South Pacific and Game Changers

contestants.name: Benjamin "Coach" Wade
contestants.bio: 53-year-old from Susanville, California. Known as Coach, he reached the final five on Survivor: Tocantins and later competed on Heroes vs. Villains and South Pacific, finishing as runner-up in South Pacific

contestants.name: Aubry Bracco
contestants.bio: 39-year-old from Hampton Falls, New Hampshire. Aubry was the runner-up of Survivor: Kaôh Rōng (Season 32). She returned for Game Changers and Edge of Extinction, known for her strategic gameplay

contestants.name: Chrissy Hofbeck
contestants.bio: 54-year-old from The Villages, Florida. On Survivor: Heroes vs Healers vs Hustlers (Season 35), Chrissy reached the Final Tribal Council and tied the women’s record by winning four immunity challenges

contestants.name: Christian Hubicki
contestants.bio: 39-year-old from Tallahassee, Florida. A robotics professor and puzzle whiz, Christian played on Survivor: David vs. Goliath, where he became a fan favorite and reached the final seven

contestants.name: Angelina Keeley
contestants.bio: 35-year-old from San Diego, California. Angelina competed on Survivor: David vs. Goliath and made it to the Final Tribal Council, but she received no votes and finished as second runner-up

contestants.name: Mike White
contestants.bio: 54-year-old from Hanalei, Hawaii. An accomplished writer and actor, Mike was the runner-up of Survivor: David vs. Goliath. He is also known for creating the HBO series The White Lotus

contestants.name: Rick Devens
contestants.bio: 41-year-old news anchor from Macon, Georgia. On Survivor: Edge of Extinction, Rick was voted out early but returned from the Edge and dominated challenges and strategy until being eliminated at the final four

contestants.name: Jonathan Young
contestants.bio: 32-year-old from Gulf Shores, Alabama. Jonathan competed on Survivor 42 and became known for his physical dominance in challenges, ultimately finishing in fourth place

contestants.name: Dee Valladares
contestants.bio: 28-year-old from Miami, Florida. Dee won Survivor 45, emerging as the Sole Survivor of that season

contestants.name: Emily Flippen
contestants.bio: 30-year-old investment analyst from Laurel, Maryland. Emily appeared on Survivor 45 and was voted out at the final seven after an underdog run

contestants.name: Q Burdette
contestants.bio: 31-year-old from Germantown, Tennessee. Q competed on Survivor 46 as a member of the Yanu tribe and finished in sixth place

contestants.name: Tiffany Nicole Ervin
contestants.bio: 34-year-old from Los Angeles, California. Tiffany played on Survivor 46 as part of the Yanu tribe and was voted out at the final eight

contestants.name: Charlie Davis
contestants.bio: 27-year-old medical student from Boston, Massachusetts. Charlie reached the Final Tribal Council of Survivor 46 and finished as the runner-up

contestants.name: Genevieve Mushaluk
contestants.bio: 34-year-old from Winnipeg, Manitoba. Genevieve was a strategic threat on Survivor 47, leading alliances until she was voted out at the final five

contestants.name: Kamilla Karthigesu
contestants.bio: 31-year-old from Foster City, California. On Survivor 48 she formed a quiet alliance with eventual winner Kyle Fraser and made it to the final four before losing the fire-making challenge

contestants.name: Kyle Fraser
contestants.bio: 31-year-old from Brooklyn, New York. Kyle dominated Survivor 48 with strategic and social play, earning the title of Sole Survivor

contestants.name: Joseph "Joe" Hunter
contestants.bio: 45-year-old from West Sacramento, California. Joe reached the Final Tribal Council on Survivor 48 and placed third

contestants.name: Rizo Velovic
contestants.bio: 25-year-old from Yonkers, New York. On Survivor 49, Rizo fought his way to the final four but lost the fire-making challenge to the eventual winner

contestants.name: Savannah Louie
contestants.bio: 31-year-old from Atlanta, Georgia. Savannah became the most recent Sole Survivor by winning Survivor 49
